# PadrĂµes de Services

## Quando Usar Services

Services sĂŁo para **regras de negĂłcio complexas** que:
- Envolvem mĂşltiplos Repositories
- Precisam de transactions (operaĂ§Ăµes multi-tabela)
- TĂŞm lĂłgica condicional complexa (state machines, validaĂ§Ăµes de negĂłcio)
- Integram com serviĂ§os externos (webhooks, email, filas)
- Processam dados em batch

> Se Ă© um CRUD simples, o Controller + Repository bastam. NĂŁo criar Service desnecessĂˇrio.

## Estrutura Base

```typescript
import EntityRepository from 'App/Repositories/{Domain}/EntityRepository';
import RelatedRepository from 'App/Repositories/{Domain}/RelatedRepository';
import HttpException from 'App/Exceptions/HttpException';
import Logger from '@ioc:Adonis/Core/Logger';
import Database from '@ioc:Adonis/Lucid/Database';

export class EntityService {
  private entityRepository: EntityRepository;
  private relatedRepository: RelatedRepository;

  constructor() {
    this.entityRepository = new EntityRepository();
    this.relatedRepository = new RelatedRepository();
  }

  public async processEntity(data: ProcessData): Promise<Entity> {
    // 1. ValidaĂ§Ăµes de negĂłcio
    await this.validateBusinessRules(data);

    // 2. Transaction para operaĂ§Ăµes multi-tabela
    const trx = await Database.transaction();
    try {
      const result = await this.executeLogic(data, trx);
      await trx.commit();

      // 3. AĂ§Ăµes pĂłs-processamento (fora da transaction)
      await this.postProcess(result);

      return result;
    } catch (error) {
      await trx.rollback();
      Logger.error('EntityService.processEntity failed', { error, data });
      throw error;
    }
  }

  private async validateBusinessRules(data: ProcessData): Promise<void> {
    const entity = await this.entityRepository.getOrFail(data.entityId);

    if (entity.statusId !== StatusEnum.ACTIVE) {
      throw new HttpException('Entidade nĂŁo estĂˇ ativa para esta operaĂ§ĂŁo', 422);
    }
  }
}
```

## PadrĂŁo de State Machine (Transitions)

```typescript
export class EntityTransitionService {
  private statusCache = new Map<number, Status>();

  public async validateTransition(
    entity: Entity,
    targetStatusId: number,
    payload: TransitionPayload
  ): Promise<{ valid: boolean; errors: string[]; confirmations: string[] }> {
    const errors: string[] = [];
    const confirmations: string[] = [];

    // Validar transiĂ§ĂŁo permitida
    const allowedTransitions = this.getAllowedTransitions(entity.statusId);
    if (!allowedTransitions.includes(targetStatusId)) {
      errors.push('TransiĂ§ĂŁo de status nĂŁo permitida');
      return { valid: false, errors, confirmations };
    }

    // Validar campos obrigatĂłrios para o status alvo
    if (targetStatusId === StatusEnum.APPROVED && !payload.orderNumber) {
      errors.push('NĂşmero do pedido Ă© obrigatĂłrio para aprovaĂ§ĂŁo');
    }

    return { valid: errors.length === 0, errors, confirmations };
  }
}
```

## Nomenclatura de Services

| Tipo                  | PadrĂŁo               | Exemplo                  |
| --------------------- | -------------------- | ------------------------ |
| DomĂ­nio               | `{Domain}Service`    | `OrderService`           |
